{"tid":2155917,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"如果貓狗突然唔想食平時食開嘅糧，入嚟睇睇","createTime":"2020-08-14T05:58:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T03:07:55.000Z","uid":19087,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6859420788440fbfeb05dca6ddf5df094cb54ac2","tid":2155917,"uid":19087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:58:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2709111639358947\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2709111639358947&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBRxksnaRIvLJvZlYWuj0OsWg%3D&h=1a934adc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2709111639358947</a><br />\n大家有時間可以睇下條片<br />\n原來平時儲放糧嘅方法會影響到啲糧嘅品質，從而有機會令到貓狗唔想食 <br />\n我總結下佢哋大約講咩<br />\n<br />\n1. 包裝上嘅「最佳使用時間」係代表放喺架上面嘅時間，而唔係打開咗包裝之後嘅時間<br />\n<br />\n2. 開咗嘅糧最好喺 2星期內食完。因為啲糧外加上嘅 <strong><span class=\"red\">油</span></strong> 同 <strong><span class=\"red\">肥</span></strong> 氧化之後會產生異味（我哋未必聞得出，但貓狗會。所以有時點解佢哋會無啦啦唔想食啲糧嘅原因，佢哋用緊呢啲行為話你聽啲糧可能變咗）<br />\n<br />\n3. 用嚟儲放糧嘅器皿建議係用不銹鋼、玻璃樽 或者係 印住 (<strong><span class=\"red\">#2 HDPE, #4 LDPE &amp; #5 PP</span></strong>) 嘅膠箱/ 盒。因為其他類型嘅塑膠同啲 油 &amp; 肥 氧化咗之後會產生一啲有害嘅化學物質。令到貓貓狗狗唔想食，或者長期食用會對身體有害<br />\n<br />\n4. 鑵鑵都一樣。如果一次食唔晒，要另外搵嘢裝起佢，唔好就咁成鑵放入雪櫃 <br />\n<br />\n5. 儲放糧嘅時候，可以將成包糧倒入所用嘅器皿，唔好連埋個包裝一齊放。因為有啲糧嘅包裝袋嘅膠連埋啲糧被氧化都會產生有毒化學物質<br />\n<br />\n6. 佢哋建議主人們買細包啲嘅糧，可以快啲食完同 Keep 住新鮮<br />\n<br />\n7. 想啲糧Keep 住新鮮耐啲可以放入凍櫃 （但開封咗嘅都要盡快食完）<br />\n<br />\n8. 喂生肉糧嘅話，最好喺 3個月內食完<br />\n<br />\n9. 可以留返個包裝袋以防萬一包糧要回收或者有其他問題 <br />\n<br />\n另外 Dr. Karen Becker 有份參與嘅記錄片 Pet Fooled 大家有時間可以搵嚟睇下"},{"pid":"1a6c59f7a6155d11361bb0a2a9af025eebff67f4","tid":2155917,"uid":299372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T12:41:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0780292c74737d18298b7eb806e7bed13a0ce485","tid":2155917,"uid":19087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T03:59:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9fd224529a61d715df2e2f72cb0bf6aabd6ec194","tid":2155917,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T04:28:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee70c000bc5b86b5611aeadd1e82b5ae7df59885","tid":2155917,"uid":19087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T04:38:04.000Z","msg":"重要資訊<br />\n推"},{"pid":"5fa8f9e2b32d37c31a603cd10964ec4f4096ba37","tid":2155917,"uid":19087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T07:51:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e047078802aedda712eb34719e6ef8e9adbc345b","tid":2155917,"uid":19087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:00:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3171c47850576d70c155b586401969e63d8ec7b3","tid":2155917,"uid":19087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T05:53:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"95073007460bd86cc087c6eedaabd14dd6fccf59","tid":2155917,"uid":146119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T06:21:51.000Z","msg":"我隻狗連5 lbs都食好耐點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最細係得2lbs?"},{"pid":"f69441a8efcbabc9f70524b2a80b4ccde8b7e171","tid":2155917,"uid":19087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95073007460bd86cc087c6eedaabd14dd6fccf59","tid":2155917,"uid":146119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T06:21:51.000Z","msg":"我隻狗連5 lbs都食好耐點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最細係得2lbs?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:15:00.000Z","msg":"佢哋建議可以將包糧放入急凍嚟防潮濕同氧化<br />\n如果怕發毛就要拎出嚟幾日再放返入急凍 重覆咁做 <br />\n最重要都係儲放時盡量整走晒啲氧氣